{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b838172eb","title":"大字报——“怎样治校好？”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4fc2817598","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"3b838172eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"545135ab5a","name":"匿名"},{"id":"b9d6e9c96b","name":"北京政法学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b7d807a739","type":"title","text":"大字报——“怎样治校好？”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"d0faeebb23","type":"authors","text":"北京政法学院匿名","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"36a6298e1e","type":"subtitle","text":"怎样治校好？ (抄自大礼堂前)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"36f7890361","type":"paragraph","text":"教师和同学鸣放中探讨党委治校或教授治校，我看都不太好。我建议党委、各民主党派和非党的教授共同治校好。如是更好的治校方式，大家共鸣共探讨，我的意见如下：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"a934b62043","type":"paragraph","text":"在大学中成立校(院)务委员会，其组成人员：院长、教务长、各教研室主任、教授会议的代表(其中是党委、各民主党派人士、无党派人士)；其职权是决定校内重大问题。如教学和学术问题，政治思想教育等问题(代表现在党委的职权)；其活动原则是集体领导、分工负责。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"85aee19488","type":"paragraph","text":"其次成立教授会议，发挥教授们的积极作用、集中他们对教学与学术等问题的意见。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"d1850918b9","type":"paragraph","text":"党委、各民主党派和非党教授共同治校优点如下：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"486fd64f68","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)加强党委、各民主党派和非党人士合作，同时也贯彻党的领导，又能和群众共商院内大事。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"d3b6c177ec","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)确定了各民主党派在学院的地位，同时也能发挥他们的作用，教授们能发挥主动性及积极性。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"bd0d4d8560","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)分工负责，非党人士有职有权。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"7974c09301","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)限制或至少少犯官僚主义、宗派主义及主观主义。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"3c24f0e20b","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)避免外行人讨论内行人的事，闭门造车费力不讨好。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"bf3b8f1b3d","type":"paragraph","text":"最后我再一次建议老师们，共同鸣放共同探讨，看看哪种治校方式好，那种较好，那种最好。我建议党委把我们鸣放的意见反映到中央有关部门研究。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"},{"id":"58d51d3672","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《北京政法学院右派分子言行汇编》(第3部分)(北京政法学院，1957年10月)。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb"}],"page":{"id":"b8f62f0b84","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3b838172eb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}